    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆◆ 什么是MechNest?◆◆</h2><br>MechNest是一个个人发展，也是我的第一个游戏。<br><br>它是roguelike、射击和砍杀元素的平衡组合。<br><br>标题的意思是 &quot;机械人的巢穴&quot;。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/deabc7c331839a1ea5711ac5a44c0860.poster.avif?t=1713077723\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/deabc7c331839a1ea5711ac5a44c0860.webm?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/deabc7c331839a1ea5711ac5a44c0860.mp4?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆◆Roguelike◆◆</h2><br>地牢和敌人的角色是随机产生的，增强的物品不能带入下一个游戏（permadeath）。<br>通过击败老板，新的技能和自定义外观元素被解锁。<br>没有关卡或多人游戏元素。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/da5fba89ae1b560c391e8a0c06b8a912.poster.avif?t=1713077723\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/da5fba89ae1b560c391e8a0c06b8a912.webm?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/da5fba89ae1b560c391e8a0c06b8a912.mp4?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆◆射击◆◆</h2><br>在MechNest的主要射击中，没有锁定或归位元素。<br>重点是射击，而不是行动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/a460f336f96a14dbfd941b8d65c3ff76.poster.avif?t=1713077723\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/a460f336f96a14dbfd941b8d65c3ff76.webm?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/a460f336f96a14dbfd941b8d65c3ff76.mp4?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆◆Hack and Slash◆◆</h2><br>除了 困难 模式，游戏被设计成令人振奋而不是紧张的。<br>HP和盾牌会自动恢复，所以你可以面对成群结队的敌人。<br>游戏的核心是与一个又一个出现的敌人作战。<br>没有任何故事元素。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/ad433dafae3e03695fa4079b10a2eaff.poster.avif?t=1713077723\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/ad433dafae3e03695fa4079b10a2eaff.webm?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/ad433dafae3e03695fa4079b10a2eaff.mp4?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆◆我们需要您的支持!◆◆</h2><br>MechNest只由两个人经营，即开发者和推广者。<br>如果你喜欢Mecnest，请通过分享和评论支持我们。<br>在Twitter上，我们鼓励你使用#MechNest的标签。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/5984394295056364ab2a6a553c33c16c.poster.avif?t=1713077723\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/5984394295056364ab2a6a553c33c16c.webm?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1379120/extras/5984394295056364ab2a6a553c33c16c.mp4?t=1713077723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
